    <item>
      <title>沃尔夫的罗斯预计就业报告中会出现很多“噪音”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-25/wolfe-s-roth-expects-lots-of-noise-in-jobs-report-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Wolfe Research 的 Stephanie Roth 预计 10 月份就业报告将增加 70,000 个。华尔街的预期是增加 120,000 个。Roth 解释了她对“彭博监测”的预期为何如此之低。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-25/wolfe-s-roth-expects-lots-of-noise-in-jobs-report-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 13:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
